                            <comment id="10310" author="juergen.hoeller" created="Mon, 19 Apr 2004 21:14:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;IMO, AopUtils.getAllInterfaces is correct as-is, but DelegatingIntroductionInterceptor needs to check whether a given interface is &lt;b&gt;assignable&lt;/b&gt; from one of the published interfaces. This will correctly detect superinterfaces. I&apos;ve just applied the change and added corresponding test cases. Juergen&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
